WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 32=

01:53.410 --> 01:55.490
We should also thank Wang Yuanjing.

01:55.490 --> 01:57.770
While practicing refining pills,

01:57.770 --> 01:59.570
he taught me a method to extract

02:00.050 --> 02:03.020
the essence of plants using vapor.

02:03.490 --> 02:04.980
The Night Orchid essence

02:04.980 --> 02:06.930
can permanently sustain the effect.

02:13.380 --> 02:14.660
Done!

02:17.940 --> 02:18.780
Granny,

02:19.170 --> 02:20.570
do you want to leave the marsh?

02:23.010 --> 02:24.130
What is this?

02:24.130 --> 02:25.500
Sticky.

02:25.500 --> 02:26.610
Just drink it.

02:27.500 --> 02:29.100
In half an incense stick's time,

02:29.820 --> 02:31.500
we'll see if it works.

02:56.820 --> 02:57.980
Zhao,

02:59.780 --> 03:01.570
did Mr. Mu

03:01.570 --> 03:03.100
apologize to you later?

03:05.170 --> 03:06.850
He nearly angered me to death.

03:06.850 --> 03:08.380
Still young after all.

03:08.850 --> 03:11.380
Not as good as Master Zhengyang.

03:12.220 --> 03:13.260
Granny Jiang,

03:13.890 --> 03:16.660
how did Master Zhengyang
apologize to my aunt?

03:17.850 --> 03:19.290
He...

03:20.820 --> 03:21.660
Pingshu.

03:24.500 --> 03:25.340
I was wrong.

03:26.145 --> 03:27.445
I'll listen to you in everything.

03:29.610 --> 03:30.450
Pingshu!

03:30.660 --> 03:31.500
Coming!

03:39.060 --> 03:39.900
That's it?

03:40.290 --> 03:41.980
Young couples argue.

03:41.980 --> 03:43.500
It's normal.

03:44.380 --> 03:46.100
Master Zhengyang deserved it.

03:46.380 --> 03:47.290
Men must be taught

03:47.610 --> 03:49.660
when disobedient.

03:52.170 --> 03:53.540
What happened

03:53.540 --> 03:55.170
to them after?

03:55.730 --> 03:56.780
Later,

03:58.060 --> 04:00.660
Aunt found out Master Zhengyang
had deceived her,

04:01.410 --> 04:03.010
and they separated.

04:03.610 --> 04:04.940
Later,

04:05.380 --> 04:06.940
Aunt killed a fiend

04:08.380 --> 04:09.730
and was seriously injured.

04:10.500 --> 04:11.730
Five years ago,

04:12.540 --> 04:13.690
she passed away.

04:16.900 --> 04:17.740
Then,

04:19.140 --> 04:20.410
what happened

04:21.020 --> 04:22.700
between you and Mr. Mu?

04:23.610 --> 04:24.730
We...

04:26.810 --> 04:27.850
can't go back.

04:28.170 --> 04:29.700
If so,

04:30.490 --> 04:31.900
move forward.

04:43.020 --> 04:43.860
Granny,

04:44.220 --> 04:45.580
let me check your pulse.

04:49.140 --> 04:49.980
Granny Jiang,

04:50.580 --> 04:51.980
tell everyone.

04:51.980 --> 04:54.050
You can leave the marsh.

04:59.900 --> 05:01.220
Personally,

05:01.540 --> 05:03.170
this stab brings satisfaction.

05:03.730 --> 05:05.045
This medicine was used by Mr. Mu

05:05.056 --> 05:06.580
to treat your injuries.

05:06.850 --> 05:08.780
Now, returning it settles everything.

05:08.780 --> 05:09.730
What does that mean?

05:10.723 --> 05:12.796
The Young Master considers everything
for Miss Cai.

05:13.140 --> 05:14.580
Now, he's injured,

05:14.580 --> 05:16.020
without a single kind word.

05:16.020 --> 05:17.062
Your Six Sects always say

05:17.073 --> 05:18.370
the Li members are cruel.

05:18.370 --> 05:19.810
You are the truly venomous ones.

05:21.170 --> 05:22.040
How is he?

05:22.140 --> 05:23.050
How is he?

05:23.490 --> 05:24.980
His poison hasn't healed,

05:24.980 --> 05:26.126
and now, he has new injuries.

05:26.810 --> 05:27.780
What do you think?

05:32.020 --> 05:33.700
Since you brought the ointment,

05:34.020 --> 05:35.340
deliver it to him personally.

05:37.170 --> 05:38.010
Fan,

05:38.410 --> 05:39.730
help us get some antidote herbs.

05:40.540 --> 05:41.410
Let's go.

05:41.410 --> 05:43.020
Why? I'm not going.

05:43.700 --> 05:44.540
Go away.

05:59.540 --> 06:01.353
Aren't you supposed to leave
with Song Yuzhi?

06:02.140 --> 06:03.340
Why come back for me?

06:03.980 --> 06:04.900
The Ziwei Method

06:05.490 --> 06:06.900
can confuse the mind,

06:07.490 --> 06:08.490
disrupt the meridians,

06:09.100 --> 06:10.140
and cause sudden death.

06:13.540 --> 06:14.540
You already knew.

06:14.980 --> 06:16.850
Some physicians treating Nie Hengcheng

06:17.490 --> 06:18.730
were loyal to the Mu clan.

06:20.250 --> 06:21.410
So, my father knew

06:21.780 --> 06:23.100
all along.

06:24.050 --> 06:25.250
Yet you still practiced?

06:25.250 --> 06:26.610
Nie Zhe was just a puppet.

06:27.580 --> 06:28.610
The man in black

06:29.140 --> 06:30.410
was the one who killed my father

06:31.220 --> 06:32.730
and Mr. Chang.

06:32.980 --> 06:34.406
I didn't stop you from catching him,

06:35.170 --> 06:36.212
but that doesn't require

06:36.223 --> 06:37.410
the Ziwei Method.

06:37.810 --> 06:38.930
If you keep practicing,

06:39.170 --> 06:40.443
you won't live past three years.

06:41.100 --> 06:42.170
You worry about me?

06:48.730 --> 06:51.170
Are you here to apply medicine to me?

06:52.290 --> 06:54.010
I just don't want
to see you die too early.

06:55.610 --> 06:57.020
With my current injuries,

06:57.020 --> 06:59.250
do you want me
to apply the medicine myself?

07:09.100 --> 07:12.100
Had I known this could keep you,

07:14.220 --> 07:16.050
I should've taken more cuts from you.

07:16.490 --> 07:18.100
Had I known you'd pester me like this,

07:19.700 --> 07:20.780
I'd never have let you

07:20.780 --> 07:21.853
move into Chunling Cottage.

07:27.340 --> 07:28.290
If so,

07:30.220 --> 07:32.020
I wouldn't have worried my parents

07:33.490 --> 07:34.810
or brought shame to the sect.

07:35.780 --> 07:37.040
During this year of confinement,

07:37.980 --> 07:39.220
I often think

07:41.540 --> 07:42.700
that if I hadn't met you,

07:43.410 --> 07:44.900
would I have already been living

07:45.780 --> 07:47.170
the peaceful life

07:47.170 --> 07:48.700
I wanted?

07:49.540 --> 07:51.170
Would I be freer

07:52.490 --> 07:53.330
and happier?

07:54.220 --> 07:55.250
You regret it?

07:55.700 --> 07:57.170
But there's no medicine for regret.

07:59.580 --> 08:00.900
People must pay the price

08:00.900 --> 08:01.900
for their choices.

08:03.050 --> 08:04.263
Seven lashes of the Python Whip

08:04.490 --> 08:06.700
were the price I paid
for defying my sect.

08:07.780 --> 08:08.930
The stab in your chest

08:10.020 --> 08:12.170
is the price you paid for using me.

08:13.220 --> 08:14.370
The Cais

08:14.900 --> 08:15.900
live without regrets.

08:16.780 --> 08:18.140
Love is love.

08:18.780 --> 08:20.370
Hate is hate.

08:21.170 --> 08:22.700
I did love you,

08:23.020 --> 08:24.170
but I loved even more

08:24.780 --> 08:26.900
the person I was when I loved you.

08:29.290 --> 08:30.130
Mu Qingyan,

08:31.660 --> 08:32.700
people can plan,

08:33.580 --> 08:34.420
persist,

08:35.610 --> 08:36.980
and even obsess,

08:37.890 --> 08:39.370
but you must see the cost

08:39.370 --> 08:40.420
behind obsession.

08:41.060 --> 08:42.700
Know when to stop losses.

08:43.010 --> 08:44.060
At least,

08:44.060 --> 08:46.300
know how to protect yourself.

08:49.820 --> 08:51.490
Stop practicing the Ziwei Method.

08:55.180 --> 08:56.580
I'll start over with you.

09:08.420 --> 09:09.566
Hurry! Burn the Night Orchid!

09:10.100 --> 09:10.940
Hurry!

09:11.530 --> 09:12.730
Burn the Night Orchid!

09:12.730 --> 09:13.820
Young Master,

09:13.820 --> 09:14.820
bad news.

09:14.831 --> 09:16.304
Miss Cai is burning the Night Orchid.

09:18.010 --> 09:19.300
I'll definitely burn it.

09:19.890 --> 09:21.180
Even if I die, I'll stop you.

09:22.060 --> 09:23.250
Does the promise you made

09:23.250 --> 09:24.420
still count?

09:24.420 --> 09:25.420
What promise?

09:25.420 --> 09:27.610
If I give up on the Ziwei Method,

09:28.250 --> 09:29.420
you will stay by my side,

09:29.940 --> 09:30.940
as you promised.

10:07.300 --> 10:09.770
Xingjia has land and a shop.

10:09.770 --> 10:11.300
He can take care of you.

10:15.580 --> 10:16.610
Let's go, Granny.

10:18.490 --> 10:19.330
Follow us!

10:23.580 --> 10:24.530
Mr. Mu,

10:24.530 --> 10:26.300
Yuzhi and I have other matters.

10:26.300 --> 10:27.186
We'll leave first.

10:27.197 --> 10:29.077
Are you going to investigate
the corpse slaves?

10:29.420 --> 10:30.260
I'll go with you.

10:30.490 --> 10:31.650
Master will arrive soon.

10:32.220 --> 10:34.010
If he finds Zhao with you,

10:34.010 --> 10:35.180
there will be trouble.

10:36.060 --> 10:37.650
You may not know,

10:37.940 --> 10:39.220
but a year ago, that whipping

10:39.610 --> 10:41.100
almost cost Zhao her life.

10:43.770 --> 10:45.220
This is our Six Sects' matter.

10:47.420 --> 10:48.340
You need not worry.

10:48.850 --> 10:49.690
Farewell.

10:54.900 --> 10:57.500
(Guangtian Sect, Desheng Hall)

11:01.180 --> 11:02.220
There's no proof.

11:02.850 --> 11:03.820
We should get evidence

11:04.220 --> 11:05.420
before seeing Master.

11:05.700 --> 11:06.850
You wretched girl.

11:07.130 --> 11:08.530
What are you thinking?

11:09.530 --> 11:11.060
You haven't married Song,

11:11.250 --> 11:12.350
yet you disobey your father.

11:12.730 --> 11:13.570
Who taught you?

11:14.420 --> 11:16.490
Grandfather just died,

11:16.490 --> 11:18.180
yet Father told me to marry Song Xiuzhi

11:18.180 --> 11:19.890
and forced me to poison him secretly.

11:20.370 --> 11:21.650
I can't obey.

11:22.370 --> 11:24.340
If I can't control you,

11:24.340 --> 11:25.610
your father will.

11:26.650 --> 11:27.490
Who?

11:30.300 --> 11:31.140
Go.

11:34.540 --> 11:35.500
(Rainlight Chamber)

11:35.530 --> 11:37.940
Song Xiuzhi isn't simple either.

11:39.890 --> 11:40.730
Wretched girl.

11:40.980 --> 11:42.420
Ungrateful like her mother.

11:42.700 --> 11:44.700
We must use the Control Powder

11:44.700 --> 11:46.130
to make her obedient.

11:46.700 --> 11:48.770
She'll have to drug him.

11:50.650 --> 11:51.490
Master You,

11:51.850 --> 11:52.770
why are you here?

11:52.770 --> 11:53.610
Mr. Song,

11:54.010 --> 11:55.580
don't think we were following you.

11:55.890 --> 11:57.650
To be clear, we arrived first.

11:58.010 --> 11:58.850
Miss Cai,

11:58.987 --> 12:00.867
the Young Master has questions
for Yang Heying.

12:01.010 --> 12:01.963
We just arrived as well.

12:02.580 --> 12:03.420
Lord Yang.

12:04.370 --> 12:05.210
Mu...

12:07.940 --> 12:08.780
Chief Mu.

12:09.060 --> 12:09.900
Lord Yang,

12:10.340 --> 12:11.250
long time no see.

12:11.980 --> 12:13.248
Last year's plan to capture you

12:13.259 --> 12:14.420
was not my idea.

12:14.420 --> 12:15.730
Every debt has its debtor.

12:15.730 --> 12:16.650
Don't act rashly.

12:16.650 --> 12:18.060
Last year, I was caught

12:18.060 --> 12:19.420
because I was outmatched.

12:19.420 --> 12:20.490
I have nothing to say.

12:21.130 --> 12:22.250
Today, I didn't come

12:22.250 --> 12:23.300
for revenge.

12:23.940 --> 12:26.060
I just have two questions for you.

12:26.530 --> 12:29.250
Speak truthfully,

12:31.610 --> 12:32.980
and I won't kill anyone.

12:34.220 --> 12:35.146
What are the questions?

12:35.730 --> 12:37.340
What happened to the corpse slaves

12:37.940 --> 12:39.580
near Guangtian Sect?

12:39.820 --> 12:40.875
Isn't making corpse slaves

12:40.886 --> 12:42.650
a secret of your sect?

12:42.650 --> 12:43.610
How would I know?

12:43.850 --> 12:44.690
If you want answers,

12:44.820 --> 12:46.130
you should ask Song Shijun.

12:47.060 --> 12:49.300
The play you and Song Xiuzhi staged

12:49.610 --> 12:51.010
was impressive.

12:51.490 --> 12:53.490
But you missed one key point:

12:53.890 --> 12:54.890
I've killed all

12:54.890 --> 12:56.820
of Nie Zhe's subordinates

12:57.130 --> 12:58.980
who knew the corpse slave method.

12:59.850 --> 13:00.730
Speak!

13:00.730 --> 13:01.850
Was it Yu Huiyin

13:03.300 --> 13:04.850
or the man in black?

13:05.650 --> 13:07.300
I don't know what you're saying.

13:08.420 --> 13:09.260
Guanyue.

13:10.300 --> 13:11.140
He's asking for me.

13:15.130 --> 13:16.300
Evil will be punished by evil.

13:16.650 --> 13:17.490
Your gentlemanly act

13:17.490 --> 13:18.580
is useless on them.

13:19.100 --> 13:20.220
Since they're willing to act,

13:20.610 --> 13:21.850
let them question first.

13:22.770 --> 13:23.610
Young Master.

13:25.070 --> 13:25.940
What are you doing?

13:25.940 --> 13:26.940
What do you want?

13:26.940 --> 13:28.020
- Chief Mu.
- Tianci.

13:28.020 --> 13:28.870
Chief Mu.

13:28.880 --> 13:30.340
Honey, just speak.

13:30.340 --> 13:31.890
Saving the child comes first.

13:32.650 --> 13:33.580
Chief Mu,

13:34.100 --> 13:36.010
I don't know anything

13:36.010 --> 13:37.340
about Yu or Nie.

13:37.490 --> 13:38.370
You don't have

13:38.370 --> 13:40.530
to falsely pin the corpse slaves on me.

13:40.980 --> 13:41.820
Lord Yang,

13:42.180 --> 13:43.300
don't regret this later.

13:44.480 --> 13:45.340
Mr. Mu, you're asking

13:45.340 --> 13:46.730
about six months ago, right?

13:47.340 --> 13:48.180
Six months ago,

13:48.770 --> 13:49.940
Father suddenly cleared

13:49.940 --> 13:51.650
a secluded yard behind the mountain.

13:51.650 --> 13:52.580
Soon after,

13:52.580 --> 13:54.820
villagers went missing repeatedly,

13:54.820 --> 13:56.490
causing widespread panic.

13:56.490 --> 13:58.650
The villagers asked Father
to investigate.

13:58.650 --> 14:00.260
He agreed in words,

14:00.260 --> 14:01.130
but the next day,

14:01.130 --> 14:02.770
the yard

14:02.770 --> 14:05.060
was burned completely.

14:05.060 --> 14:07.300
Mother, for some reason, went there

14:07.300 --> 14:08.700
and was gravely injured.

14:10.130 --> 14:10.970
She...

14:11.370 --> 14:13.250
She died from pain.

14:13.650 --> 14:15.250
So, they previously experimented

14:16.250 --> 14:18.650
on nearby villagers.

14:18.650 --> 14:20.130
Sensing trouble,

14:20.130 --> 14:21.530
they destroyed the evidence

14:21.530 --> 14:22.980
and moved the corpse slave workshop

14:22.980 --> 14:24.700
to a more remote Mount Qimu.

14:24.700 --> 14:26.340
I've always wanted to know, Father:

14:26.940 --> 14:28.530
What happened in that yard?

14:28.530 --> 14:30.250
Why did Mother go there?

14:31.010 --> 14:32.940
If you made the corpse slaves

14:33.700 --> 14:35.060
and killed my grandfather,

14:35.370 --> 14:37.770
uncles, aunts, and cousins?

14:37.770 --> 14:38.980
Girl, stop spouting nonsense.

14:40.580 --> 14:41.420
Lord Yang,

14:42.490 --> 14:44.300
you know what I'm capable of.

14:44.730 --> 14:45.850
My arrival means

14:45.850 --> 14:47.300
I already know

14:47.300 --> 14:48.370
the facts.

14:49.490 --> 14:51.010
Why still deny it?

14:51.530 --> 14:53.010
If you know everything,

14:53.340 --> 14:54.650
why ask me?

14:55.890 --> 14:58.010
You killed Grandfather?

14:58.850 --> 14:59.770
What about Mother?

15:00.650 --> 15:02.490
Was her death truly accidental?

15:04.130 --> 15:04.970
Guanyue.

15:09.370 --> 15:10.210
Little one,

15:10.420 --> 15:13.580
come with me for candy.

15:13.580 --> 15:14.530
I don't want candy!

15:14.530 --> 15:15.650
I don't!

15:15.650 --> 15:16.730
- Mother!
- Tianci!

15:16.730 --> 15:17.580
Honey,

15:18.890 --> 15:20.220
just say it.

15:20.220 --> 15:21.730
Tianci is your only heir.

15:21.730 --> 15:23.490
Nothing can happen to him.

15:28.890 --> 15:30.580
Six months ago, someone came to me

15:30.980 --> 15:32.580
and taught me the corpse slave method.

15:33.010 --> 15:34.770
I only tried it out of curiosity

15:34.770 --> 15:35.980
and never used it

15:35.980 --> 15:36.940
on your sect.

15:37.420 --> 15:38.673
This has nothing to do with you.

15:38.770 --> 15:39.610
Who was he?

15:39.810 --> 15:41.696
I couldn't recognize him
with his face covered.

15:42.010 --> 15:42.890
Chief Mu,

15:42.890 --> 15:44.490
our Six Sects and your sect

15:44.490 --> 15:45.940
mind our own business.

15:46.580 --> 15:48.220
I advise you not to interfere.

15:48.490 --> 15:49.683
You refined the corpse slaves.

15:50.010 --> 15:51.530
Why frame my father?

15:51.730 --> 15:52.890
You almost killed him!

15:55.610 --> 15:57.060
Song Shijun,

15:57.060 --> 15:58.940
taking your wealth for granted,

15:58.940 --> 16:00.730
looked down on our Siqi Sect

16:02.060 --> 16:03.730
and humiliated me repeatedly.

16:04.820 --> 16:06.300
I finally had a chance to see

16:06.300 --> 16:07.770
his two sons fight.

16:07.770 --> 16:09.250
Why shouldn't I act?

16:09.250 --> 16:10.220
How involved

16:10.730 --> 16:12.180
was Song Xiuzhi in all this?

16:13.010 --> 16:14.340
Your brother

16:15.010 --> 16:16.730
truly hid his nature.

16:17.060 --> 16:18.580
Even I almost misjudged him.

16:18.690 --> 16:19.610
I only wanted

16:19.610 --> 16:21.130
to strengthen Siqi Sect

16:21.130 --> 16:22.300
and vent some anger.

16:22.890 --> 16:23.940
But your brother,

16:23.940 --> 16:25.130
my good son-in-law,

16:25.650 --> 16:27.530
has ambitions far beyond mine.

16:27.530 --> 16:29.010
Lord Song's skills

16:29.010 --> 16:29.980
are far above yours.

16:30.810 --> 16:31.700
How did you plant

16:31.700 --> 16:32.820
the Puppet Gu on him?

16:33.300 --> 16:34.490
Who really acted?

16:36.530 --> 16:38.130
Mr. Mu, since you're here,

16:38.370 --> 16:39.610
why not step out?

16:43.370 --> 16:44.210
Zhao,

16:44.490 --> 16:45.330
Yuzhi,

16:45.770 --> 16:46.610
come out.

16:47.010 --> 16:47.850
With me here,

16:48.100 --> 16:49.130
he won't dare abduct you.

17:00.650 --> 17:01.610
Lord Qi,

17:02.580 --> 17:03.940
long time no see.

17:04.220 --> 17:05.060
Master.

17:05.860 --> 17:06.700
Are you alright?

17:06.900 --> 17:08.060
- I'm fine.
- Master,

17:08.660 --> 17:09.762
Mu Qingyan is investigating

17:09.773 --> 17:10.900
the corpse slaves with us.

17:11.380 --> 17:12.220
This matter

17:12.660 --> 17:13.730
was orchestrated

17:14.810 --> 17:16.900
by Yang Heying and my brother.

17:17.180 --> 17:18.020
Nonsense.

17:18.620 --> 17:19.770
That fiend threatened me

17:19.770 --> 17:20.810
with my wife and child;

17:20.810 --> 17:22.620
I only told lies to stall him.

17:22.620 --> 17:24.050
Changing words again.

17:24.050 --> 17:25.010
You're talking nonsense.

17:27.420 --> 17:28.260
Xiuzhi,

17:29.770 --> 17:31.420
do you have anything to say?

17:31.420 --> 17:32.260
Yuzhi,

17:33.140 --> 17:34.730
don't fall for the demonic sect's trap.

17:35.290 --> 17:36.330
How could I harm Father?

17:37.570 --> 17:38.410
Lord Qi,

17:38.660 --> 17:39.893
repel the outside threat first.

17:40.050 --> 17:41.079
Don't let the demonic sect

17:41.090 --> 17:42.770
mock the Six Sects.

17:42.940 --> 17:44.250
Xiuzhi is right.

17:45.420 --> 17:46.260
Yuzhi,

17:46.490 --> 17:48.380
your father's life is uncertain.

17:48.660 --> 17:50.490
Do we fight each other

17:50.490 --> 17:52.250
in front of the demonic sect?

17:53.980 --> 17:54.860
Master Xiuzhi,

17:55.290 --> 17:57.810
Yang Heying already admitted it.

17:58.050 --> 17:59.420
You're involved

17:59.420 --> 18:00.980
with that fiend.

18:00.980 --> 18:02.342
You worked with the demonic sect,

18:02.353 --> 18:03.770
making my husband admit it.

18:04.090 --> 18:06.140
You traitorous little girl!

18:08.900 --> 18:10.490
Speak nonsense again,

18:11.490 --> 18:12.700
and face the consequences.

18:16.490 --> 18:17.330
Master,

18:19.290 --> 18:20.620
handling sect matters is urgent.

18:21.220 --> 18:22.246
Don't bother with him now.

18:23.570 --> 18:24.930
- Alright.
- Lord Qi,

18:25.660 --> 18:26.980
we can't let them go.

18:26.980 --> 18:28.530
You can clarify

18:28.530 --> 18:30.380
how Leader Huang actually died.

18:30.380 --> 18:32.490
What? As I already said,

18:32.490 --> 18:34.250
it was just to deceive the fiend.

18:34.250 --> 18:35.660
How would I know the truth?

18:37.290 --> 18:39.140
But the day you came to confront,

18:39.140 --> 18:41.800
you spoke as if you saw
Lord Song kill him.

18:41.800 --> 18:42.650
Oh,

18:42.650 --> 18:43.900
you also said

18:43.900 --> 18:46.770
Lord Song hurt Master Xiuzhi.

18:46.770 --> 18:47.940
You depicted

18:47.940 --> 18:49.420
the story vividly,

18:49.420 --> 18:50.570
as if you saw it.

18:51.010 --> 18:52.010
I felt strange.

18:52.380 --> 18:53.730
It's supposed to be a secret.

18:54.900 --> 18:56.900
Lord Yang, how did you know?

18:58.290 --> 18:59.530
Song Xiuzhi told me.

18:59.530 --> 19:00.380
Ask him.

19:00.380 --> 19:01.980
His injuries can't be fake.

19:02.420 --> 19:03.260
Lord Yang,

19:04.420 --> 19:05.730
Father injured me by mistake,

19:06.420 --> 19:07.770
but I never said

19:07.770 --> 19:09.620
he killed Leader Huang.

19:09.620 --> 19:10.810
You told me Father killed

19:11.330 --> 19:12.940
Leader Huang's whole family.

19:13.180 --> 19:14.250
I didn't believe it,

19:14.810 --> 19:16.380
but you made me confront him.

19:16.640 --> 19:17.490
In hindsight,

19:17.490 --> 19:19.620
Father's actions were strange.

19:19.980 --> 19:20.820
Lord Yang,

19:21.180 --> 19:22.220
what exactly did you do

19:22.566 --> 19:23.986
that made Father suddenly attack me?

19:24.660 --> 19:26.490
Good, Song Xiuzhi.

19:26.900 --> 19:28.570
You wiped yourself clean.

19:28.980 --> 19:30.940
If not for letting you become the Lord,

19:30.940 --> 19:32.290
why bother?

19:33.290 --> 19:34.420
I'm Father's eldest son,

19:35.140 --> 19:36.490
qualified to be the Lord.

19:38.010 --> 19:39.660
No need for your scheming.

19:40.050 --> 19:40.980
Song Xiuzhi...

19:41.380 --> 19:42.220
Yuzhi,

19:42.660 --> 19:43.940
your brother

19:43.940 --> 19:45.140
has a great talent

19:45.700 --> 19:46.700
for acting.

19:49.290 --> 19:50.380
If you had clarified things

19:50.380 --> 19:52.010
in person that day,

19:52.409 --> 19:53.888
things wouldn't have become like this.

19:53.980 --> 19:55.330
I didn't expect that Sha Tian'er

19:55.810 --> 19:57.140
would suddenly attack Father.

19:58.380 --> 20:00.140
He must have been misled.

20:00.860 --> 20:02.730
Thinking of the massacre,

20:03.050 --> 20:04.290
he was enraged,

20:04.660 --> 20:06.250
wanting to repay with his life.

20:06.250 --> 20:08.620
Sha Tian'er wasn't a Huangsha member.

20:12.180 --> 20:13.020
Ungrateful girl.

20:14.220 --> 20:15.090
Lord Qi.

20:18.900 --> 20:20.660
This is the Huangsha disciple registry.

20:21.290 --> 20:22.980
Grandfather didn't have many disciples.

20:22.980 --> 20:24.620
I know each of them,

20:24.620 --> 20:25.940
but I've never heard

20:26.810 --> 20:28.530
of Sha Tian'er.

20:29.530 --> 20:30.700
So,

20:30.700 --> 20:31.900
Sha Tian'er

20:31.900 --> 20:33.900
was probably a trained assassin.

20:34.490 --> 20:35.810
That day, I found it odd:

20:36.490 --> 20:37.980
He was weak

20:37.980 --> 20:39.180
but fearless.

20:39.180 --> 20:40.530
Such determination

20:40.530 --> 20:41.730
is beyond normal people.

20:42.490 --> 20:44.050
If not for real hatred,

20:44.380 --> 20:46.010
he must be trained since childhood.

20:48.380 --> 20:49.220
Lord Yang,

20:50.620 --> 20:52.570
why send assassins to kill my father?

20:54.140 --> 20:55.506
I was deceived by Song Xiuzhi,

20:55.517 --> 20:57.900
only aiming to avenge
my father-in-law and brothers-in-law.

20:57.900 --> 20:59.050
You're lying.

20:59.050 --> 21:01.140
You despised Mother
for not bearing a son.

21:01.140 --> 21:02.530
You never favored her

21:03.250 --> 21:04.810
and always beat and scolded her.

21:05.220 --> 21:07.860
My grandfather and uncles
clashed with you several times.

21:07.860 --> 21:09.140
You disliked them long ago.

21:09.140 --> 21:11.140
How could you avenge them?

21:11.140 --> 21:13.700
Grandfather worried about Mother and me,

21:13.700 --> 21:15.730
brought us gifts,

21:15.730 --> 21:17.700
and described the mountain terrain.

21:18.490 --> 21:20.940
That's why you targeted Mount Qimu.

21:22.660 --> 21:23.770
Yang Heying,

21:24.090 --> 21:26.530
how did my grandfather and mother die?

21:26.530 --> 21:27.810
Ungrateful girl.

21:29.490 --> 21:30.330
Honey.

21:30.900 --> 21:31.740
Yang Heying,

21:32.490 --> 21:34.250
answer Xiaolan

21:34.660 --> 21:35.693
before losing your temper.

21:37.180 --> 21:38.020
Alright.

21:40.620 --> 21:41.460
So, today,

21:42.200 --> 21:43.050
you're determined

21:43.050 --> 21:44.810
to pin this great crime on me.

21:45.810 --> 21:47.900
But empty words mean nothing.

21:48.290 --> 21:50.180
Without evidence, I won't admit it.

21:50.180 --> 21:51.020
Lord Qi,

21:52.050 --> 21:54.050
you wouldn't coerce a confession, right?

21:55.770 --> 21:56.980
Every house has its rules.

21:57.730 --> 21:58.810
So does every sect.

21:59.530 --> 22:00.620
If anyone in the Six Sects

22:00.620 --> 22:03.530
truly committed such a heinous act,

22:03.980 --> 22:05.420
I won't forgive them.

22:06.860 --> 22:08.700
I've sent people to Mount Qimu

22:09.380 --> 22:10.770
to investigate thoroughly.

22:11.490 --> 22:13.290
With such a massive corpse slave setup,

22:14.010 --> 22:17.220
they can't clear all traces.

22:17.220 --> 22:20.290
Then I'll summon heroes

22:20.290 --> 22:21.290
in the world

22:23.330 --> 22:24.770
to confront you.

22:27.490 --> 22:28.330
Alright.

22:29.730 --> 22:30.570
I'll wait.

22:32.050 --> 22:32.890
Let's go.

22:38.180 --> 22:39.020
Miss Yang,

22:39.660 --> 22:41.140
your father may have framed my father.

22:41.620 --> 22:42.700
Such a great enmity ahead,

22:43.330 --> 22:45.140
our union seems impossible.

22:45.980 --> 22:46.860
The betrothal token...

22:52.180 --> 22:53.490
Take it back.

22:57.140 --> 22:59.220
I never wanted to marry you anyway.

23:06.700 --> 23:07.980
Lord Yang acts recklessly.

23:08.940 --> 23:10.420
Miss Yang is headstrong.

23:11.050 --> 23:12.660
Yang Heying is no good.

23:13.290 --> 23:14.130
What about you?

23:15.730 --> 23:16.679
- Yuzhi.
- Why did you

23:16.690 --> 23:18.150
accuse Father in front of everyone?

23:18.700 --> 23:19.540
Yuzhi,

23:20.090 --> 23:21.290
I was deceived.

23:22.010 --> 23:22.850
Do you remember?

23:23.570 --> 23:24.940
Initially, I didn't want to speak.

23:24.940 --> 23:26.050
You kept pressing,

23:26.490 --> 23:28.010
so I revealed what I knew.

23:28.730 --> 23:29.860
I didn't make it up.

23:30.220 --> 23:31.060
If I had known,

23:32.220 --> 23:33.250
I'd have kept quiet

23:33.620 --> 23:34.810
and hidden everything.

23:38.180 --> 23:39.420
Master Xiuzhi,

23:39.770 --> 23:40.730
impressive.

23:41.090 --> 23:43.700
You cleared yourself spotlessly.

23:44.010 --> 23:45.090
Innocent indeed.

23:45.730 --> 23:46.620
Then tomorrow,

23:46.900 --> 23:49.730
I'll hire 100 storytellers

23:50.010 --> 23:52.330
to spread the recent Guangtian events

23:52.730 --> 23:54.490
far and wide,

23:55.420 --> 23:56.660
showing everyone

23:57.250 --> 23:59.770
how cunning

23:59.770 --> 24:01.530
and despicable

24:01.530 --> 24:03.050
the honorable Master Xiuzhi is.

24:03.050 --> 24:03.940
Let's see

24:03.940 --> 24:05.250
if you can still become

24:05.250 --> 24:06.570
the Lord.

24:06.570 --> 24:08.810
What a sharp-tongued girl.

24:09.330 --> 24:10.700
Lord Qi,

24:11.180 --> 24:13.490
the Six Sects have coexisted

24:14.180 --> 24:15.570
but acted independently

24:15.570 --> 24:17.380
for 200 years.

24:18.620 --> 24:21.900
If we interfere recklessly,

24:21.900 --> 24:23.490
it may disrupt unity

24:23.490 --> 24:25.620
and let the demonic sect take advantage.

24:25.620 --> 24:26.460
Don't worry.

24:27.250 --> 24:29.090
A pigeon letter from Luoying Valley says

24:29.940 --> 24:31.420
Lord Song is gravely injured

24:31.420 --> 24:32.420
and unconscious.

24:33.180 --> 24:34.250
If that's true,

24:34.900 --> 24:36.490
even if he's alive,

24:36.490 --> 24:40.330
he may never sit as the Lord again.

24:41.290 --> 24:42.860
Lord Song has only two sons.

24:43.490 --> 24:45.050
By seniority and merit,

24:49.420 --> 24:50.730
it should be Song Xiuzhi

24:50.730 --> 24:52.050
to take the lord position.

24:55.290 --> 24:56.570
I don't think he's suitable.

24:58.490 --> 24:59.700
The most suitable is you.

24:59.700 --> 25:00.540
You...

25:00.940 --> 25:02.330
The investigation isn't over,

25:02.700 --> 25:04.010
yet you're already anxious

25:04.010 --> 25:05.180
to fight for the position?

25:05.180 --> 25:06.620
Lord Qi, please judge this.

25:06.940 --> 25:08.330
Our Guangtian affairs

25:08.330 --> 25:09.476
are none of others' business.

25:09.900 --> 25:10.740
Yuzhi,

25:11.090 --> 25:11.930
this matter

25:12.380 --> 25:13.700
requires your decision.

25:17.530 --> 25:18.620
Now that it's come to this,

25:19.940 --> 25:21.810
let's follow the old Guangtian rules.

25:24.010 --> 25:25.700
I'm willing to compete with Xiuzhi

25:27.380 --> 25:29.010
to determine the next lord.

25:37.100 --> 25:40.020
(Guangtian Sect)

25:40.900 --> 25:45.220
(Desheng Hall)

25:59.660 --> 26:01.140
Let the duel begin.

26:17.380 --> 26:18.220
Cai Zhao,

26:19.570 --> 26:21.570
Fengchi and I
just received news last night.

26:32.290 --> 26:34.050
Yuzhi hasn't fully recovered

26:34.050 --> 26:34.980
and was just poisoned.

26:35.290 --> 26:36.290
This is too unfair.

26:37.700 --> 26:38.540
By the way, Lingbo,

26:38.860 --> 26:40.620
I heard you went
to Mount Qimu for clues.

26:40.860 --> 26:41.980
Did you find any survivors?

26:44.700 --> 26:45.940
Even a corpse slave would help.

26:46.730 --> 26:47.730
Xingjia has the antidote.

26:47.970 --> 26:49.129
If we find the corpse slaves,

26:49.140 --> 26:50.940
we can learn the truth from them.

26:51.570 --> 26:52.420
Everything was burned.

26:53.010 --> 26:53.900
The whole mountain

26:53.900 --> 26:55.010
was reduced to ashes.

26:55.290 --> 26:56.730
When Lingbo and I arrived,

26:57.050 --> 26:58.570
we only saw charred skeletons.

26:59.090 --> 27:00.860
No idea how many people were gone.

27:01.180 --> 27:02.140
Huangsha Gang

27:02.330 --> 27:04.380
seems to have vanished overnight.

27:05.380 --> 27:06.570
Among the bones,

27:07.860 --> 27:09.570
there were even young kids.

27:10.860 --> 27:11.980
The perpetrators

27:12.220 --> 27:13.940
are more ruthless than the demonic sect.

27:44.810 --> 27:45.700
Master,

27:45.700 --> 27:47.010
a duel for the Lord

27:47.250 --> 27:48.290
allows hidden weapons?

27:49.010 --> 27:49.860
Why not?

27:50.490 --> 27:51.380
A duel

27:51.730 --> 27:53.770
naturally demands full effort.

28:10.810 --> 28:11.650
Yuzhi!

28:12.660 --> 28:13.500
Lingbo,

28:14.050 --> 28:14.940
if you go up now,

28:15.290 --> 28:16.860
Yuzhi will only be more embarrassed.

28:23.010 --> 28:23.850
Yuzhi,

28:24.330 --> 28:25.170
it's over.

28:28.700 --> 28:29.940
I'm outmatched.

28:30.220 --> 28:31.180
The outcome is decided.

28:31.180 --> 28:32.090
(Desheng Hall)

28:32.090 --> 28:33.220
Song Xiuzhi

28:33.700 --> 28:36.420
will become the next Lord.

28:37.730 --> 28:38.570
Everyone,

28:40.620 --> 28:42.050
any objections?

28:43.420 --> 28:44.570
I'm outmatched.

28:45.660 --> 28:46.620
Master,

28:46.620 --> 28:47.460
let's go.

28:49.900 --> 28:50.770
Today's defeat

28:51.180 --> 28:54.090
will be the step
to tomorrow's improvement.

28:59.490 --> 29:00.620
Farewell.

29:02.010 --> 29:03.050
I hope you

29:04.660 --> 29:05.730
take care of yourselves.

29:06.980 --> 29:07.820
Goodbye.

29:08.810 --> 29:09.650
Let's go.

29:18.570 --> 29:19.410
As expected, he lost.

29:20.730 --> 29:22.010
Song Yuzhi is a rising star

29:22.380 --> 29:24.220
among the young generation
of the Six Sects.

29:24.810 --> 29:26.220
But I had never heard

29:26.940 --> 29:28.330
of Song Xiuzhi.

29:28.660 --> 29:29.500
This battle

29:29.730 --> 29:31.860
was a shocking rise to fame.

29:32.290 --> 29:33.420
The opponent was prepared.

29:34.570 --> 29:36.220
Song Yuzhi should've avoided it,

29:36.660 --> 29:38.050
biding his time.

29:39.490 --> 29:40.330
However...

29:40.660 --> 29:42.180
Mr. Song

29:42.180 --> 29:43.700
has lived an easy life,

29:43.700 --> 29:45.250
admired by all since childhood.

29:45.700 --> 29:46.660
This battle

29:46.660 --> 29:47.620
was a lesson for him.

29:48.180 --> 29:50.180
Mr. Song likely understood this,

29:50.770 --> 29:52.090
but he couldn't let this strife

29:52.223 --> 29:53.412
cause chaos in Guangtian Sect.

29:53.490 --> 29:54.530
So, he reluctantly fought.

29:54.900 --> 29:55.900
All in all,

29:55.900 --> 29:57.223
it was mercy,

29:57.234 --> 29:58.460
unfit for great responsibility.

29:59.810 --> 30:00.650
Shangguan,

30:01.250 --> 30:02.490
you seem off.

30:02.490 --> 30:03.363
Which side are you on?

30:04.090 --> 30:05.330
I'm just speaking fairly.

30:05.330 --> 30:06.180
Don't you know

30:06.180 --> 30:07.250
he had his eye on Miss Cai?

30:07.250 --> 30:07.950
Now,

30:07.961 --> 30:09.010
his family is in upheaval,

30:09.010 --> 30:10.220
and he's lost to his brother.

30:10.220 --> 30:11.140
A double misfortune.

30:11.680 --> 30:12.570
What if

30:12.570 --> 30:14.180
Miss Cai softens,

30:14.180 --> 30:15.700
turning sympathy into...

30:27.290 --> 30:28.130
Talkative.

30:28.900 --> 30:29.770
Young Master,

30:29.770 --> 30:30.980
I don't mean that.

30:31.940 --> 30:32.849
Father,

30:32.860 --> 30:34.050
they are clearly scheming.

30:34.050 --> 30:35.180
And we just let it go?

30:35.570 --> 30:36.410
Lingbo,

30:36.770 --> 30:38.620
their boldness in public

30:38.620 --> 30:39.810
means everyone present

30:39.810 --> 30:42.530
is pretending ignorance.

30:43.220 --> 30:44.330
They were likely bribed

30:44.330 --> 30:45.700
by Uncle Song

30:45.700 --> 30:47.090
and Song Xiuzhi.

30:47.700 --> 30:49.010
I'm rarely at the sect.

30:49.940 --> 30:51.980
Naturally, they are closer to Xiuzhi.

30:53.620 --> 30:54.940
You weren't prepared; they were.

30:55.570 --> 30:56.770
So, you'd lose out.

30:57.180 --> 30:58.050
But for now,

30:58.290 --> 31:00.570
we must first uncover the truth
of the corpse slaves.

31:01.660 --> 31:02.500
As for this,

31:02.770 --> 31:03.610
let's wait.

31:04.660 --> 31:06.490
Master, Yang Heying has confessed.

31:07.180 --> 31:08.940
The man in black taught him

31:08.940 --> 31:09.900
the corpse slave method.

31:10.380 --> 31:12.770
This man can meddle in all sects,

31:13.140 --> 31:14.380
and in one night,

31:14.380 --> 31:16.490
clean all traces in Mount Qimu.

31:17.140 --> 31:18.490
He seems omnipotent,

31:18.860 --> 31:20.420
yet his motives remain unknown.

31:20.730 --> 31:21.810
Yu Hui escaped as well.

31:23.220 --> 31:24.810
Could they be working together?

31:25.090 --> 31:26.570
This is extremely complex.

31:27.250 --> 31:28.420
I must return to the sect

31:28.810 --> 31:30.180
to trace the full story.

31:31.620 --> 31:32.660
What are your plans?

31:33.380 --> 31:34.220
Master,

31:35.180 --> 31:36.360
I want to go to Luoying Valley

31:36.660 --> 31:37.500
to see my father.

31:38.900 --> 31:40.290
I haven't been back for a long time.

31:40.980 --> 31:42.620
I'll go with Yuzhi.

31:42.980 --> 31:43.726
Good.

31:43.737 --> 31:45.250
At least you have company on the road.

31:48.380 --> 31:49.220
What about you two?

31:50.860 --> 31:52.490
Will you continue your wander

31:52.490 --> 31:53.860
or return?

31:53.860 --> 31:54.700
- Return.
- Return.

32:10.700 --> 32:11.540
Master,

32:11.860 --> 32:13.180
I wish to formally propose

32:13.490 --> 32:14.730
to marry Lingbo.

32:27.180 --> 32:28.250
I know it's not

32:28.250 --> 32:29.380
the best timing,

32:29.380 --> 32:30.420
given Yuzhi just...

32:30.420 --> 32:31.260
No.

32:31.980 --> 32:32.820
I'm happy.

32:33.380 --> 32:34.220
Congratulations.

32:35.660 --> 32:36.500
Yes.

32:36.700 --> 32:37.770
This is a joyous occasion.

32:38.490 --> 32:39.810
Lovers finally unite.

32:40.050 --> 32:41.140
When your wedding is set,

32:41.810 --> 32:43.083
I'll demand a celebratory drink.

32:51.570 --> 32:52.410
Father,

32:52.940 --> 32:53.780
I know

32:54.490 --> 32:55.420
I used to be willful,

32:56.050 --> 32:57.180
but now I understand.

33:01.530 --> 33:02.380
This past year,

33:02.900 --> 33:03.940
whenever I was in danger,

33:04.380 --> 33:05.900
Fengchi risked his life to save me.

33:07.980 --> 33:09.420
He was the first

33:09.420 --> 33:11.220
to value my life over his own.

33:14.620 --> 33:15.460
I want to marry him.

33:31.490 --> 33:32.330
This matter

33:33.050 --> 33:34.620
must be approved

33:35.660 --> 33:37.330
by your mother.

33:46.330 --> 33:47.180
I have

33:49.860 --> 33:50.900
no objection.

33:51.220 --> 33:52.060
Wonderful.

33:52.290 --> 33:53.380
I'll toast you with tea.

33:53.380 --> 33:54.220
Congrats to you both.

33:54.940 --> 33:55.780
Congratulations.

34:14.610 --> 34:15.470
Thank you

34:15.470 --> 34:16.530
for helping me that night.

34:19.820 --> 34:20.780
You found out.

34:22.780 --> 34:24.780
Is that why you called me here?

34:24.780 --> 34:26.530
I came to bid farewell.

34:26.530 --> 34:28.260
Where are you headed now?

34:31.090 --> 34:32.860
Yang Heying killed my mother,

34:33.420 --> 34:35.130
grandfather, and uncles.

34:36.340 --> 34:37.490
I have no family left,

34:38.260 --> 34:40.380
but I won't let them die in vain.

34:41.050 --> 34:42.380
I plan to go to Huangsha Gang

34:42.380 --> 34:43.860
to find out the truth,

34:43.860 --> 34:45.130
gather evidence,

34:45.130 --> 34:46.170
and avenge them.

34:49.610 --> 34:52.010
Siqi Sect usually wields whips.

34:52.980 --> 34:54.490
Why a blade?

34:55.010 --> 34:56.090
Actually,

34:57.010 --> 34:58.650
I admired Ms. Cai since childhood,

34:58.823 --> 35:00.892
so I convinced my mother
to let me learn the blade.

35:01.050 --> 35:02.380
Mother always indulged me,

35:02.820 --> 35:04.050
so she let me.

35:05.570 --> 35:07.340
Sadly, my talent was limited.

35:08.050 --> 35:09.900
I couldn't protect her.

35:17.490 --> 35:18.820
Since you admire Aunt,

35:19.420 --> 35:20.380
you should know

35:21.130 --> 35:22.690
why her blade is called

35:22.690 --> 35:23.690
the Sunshine Blade.

35:27.900 --> 35:28.740
Radiant sunshine

35:29.210 --> 35:30.130
means brightness

35:30.940 --> 35:31.820
and fearlessness.

35:32.490 --> 35:33.340
Go do

35:33.340 --> 35:34.180
what you want.

35:34.940 --> 35:35.980
Your skills are strong.

35:37.300 --> 35:38.170
I believe,

35:38.820 --> 35:39.940
with time,

35:41.650 --> 35:43.900
you'll carve your own path.

35:48.700 --> 35:53.300
(Luoying Valley)

35:54.490 --> 35:56.050
Your father survived

35:56.780 --> 35:57.980
but lost all inner power.

35:58.300 --> 36:01.010
He can only live as an ordinary man.

36:01.740 --> 36:03.860
Did he say who harmed him?

36:04.570 --> 36:06.300
He briefly regained consciousness once,

36:07.010 --> 36:09.490
but he was delirious,

36:09.860 --> 36:11.420
with toxin still inside.

36:12.570 --> 36:14.170
He only shouted

36:14.780 --> 36:15.620
"Unfilial"

36:16.170 --> 36:17.650
and passed out again.

36:17.650 --> 36:18.900
As for what happened,

36:19.420 --> 36:22.010
we'll have to ask when he wakes up.

36:22.340 --> 36:23.610
Thanks to you two.

36:24.170 --> 36:25.300
You saved my father.

36:26.530 --> 36:27.370
Otherwise...

36:31.170 --> 36:32.900
I don't deserve to be
my father's disciple.

36:33.490 --> 36:35.610
I almost couldn't save him.

36:36.300 --> 36:37.170
Yuzhi,

36:37.170 --> 36:38.170
life is like this.

36:38.610 --> 36:40.010
It isn't smooth sailing.

36:40.820 --> 36:42.740
You haven't fully recovered,

36:42.950 --> 36:43.820
and you've never

36:43.820 --> 36:45.940
doubted your own brother.

36:47.820 --> 36:49.170
You were unprepared.

36:49.780 --> 36:51.050
That was unavoidable.

36:52.610 --> 36:53.450
Exactly.

36:54.300 --> 36:56.530
This would happen to anyone.

36:56.530 --> 36:57.490
Don't worry.

36:57.940 --> 36:59.386
Master is the head of the Six Sects.

36:59.490 --> 37:00.530
He won't ignore this.

37:00.900 --> 37:02.170
Once Song Xiuzhi's collusion

37:02.170 --> 37:04.300
with Yang Heying is revealed,

37:05.130 --> 37:06.130
no one will follow him.

37:08.860 --> 37:09.700
Thanks, Lord Cai,

37:10.420 --> 37:11.260
Zhao.

37:11.650 --> 37:14.050
I must resolve Guangtian matters myself.

37:14.650 --> 37:15.820
This loss was my fault,

37:16.900 --> 37:18.300
but next time, I'll reclaim

37:18.740 --> 37:20.900
the lord title openly.

37:36.220 --> 37:37.780
(Tablet of Yulan, Late Mother)

37:37.780 --> 37:38.620
Mother,

37:38.940 --> 37:40.570
I had Yin Qinglian's spirit tablet

37:41.690 --> 37:43.210
thrown into the waste pond.

37:43.610 --> 37:44.740
Song Shijun had high hopes

37:45.300 --> 37:47.420
for her son Song Yuzhi,

37:48.380 --> 37:50.340
yet I defeated him.

37:50.340 --> 37:51.740
That's true.

37:51.740 --> 37:52.580
Who?

37:56.340 --> 37:57.180
Mu Qingyan.

37:57.610 --> 37:58.450
Guards!

38:00.740 --> 38:01.740
They won't make it.

38:07.980 --> 38:08.820
Lord Song,

38:10.210 --> 38:11.210
two questions for you.

38:11.530 --> 38:13.010
Good and evil never coexist.

38:14.130 --> 38:16.340
I have nothing to tell you.

38:16.690 --> 38:17.900
Good and evil never coexist?

38:20.860 --> 38:22.530
I haven't colluded with outsiders,

38:22.820 --> 38:23.980
nor harmed my father

38:24.820 --> 38:25.820
or brother.

38:26.490 --> 38:27.860
Between us,

38:27.860 --> 38:28.700
who's righteous,

38:29.420 --> 38:30.260
and who's evil?

38:30.530 --> 38:31.820
Yang Heying did it all.

38:32.010 --> 38:32.940
Since I came,

38:33.340 --> 38:35.010
I already know the full story.

38:35.690 --> 38:36.530
Tell me.

38:36.980 --> 38:38.553
Who taught you the corpse slave method,

38:38.980 --> 38:40.170
wounded Song Shijun,

38:40.530 --> 38:42.530
and helped you plan

38:43.530 --> 38:44.650
the power grab?

38:49.780 --> 38:53.220
(Tablet of Yulan, Late Mother)

38:55.570 --> 38:56.860
Guangtian lords

38:57.690 --> 38:59.050
took multiple concubines

38:59.900 --> 39:00.840
and bore many children.

39:01.570 --> 39:03.820
Since Yin Qinglian married Song Shijun,

39:04.420 --> 39:05.650
she had no more children.

39:05.980 --> 39:07.940
Even the concubines vanished.

39:08.380 --> 39:09.780
Did that person tell you

39:10.130 --> 39:12.170
Yin Qinglian killed them all?

39:14.050 --> 39:15.090
Yes.

39:24.380 --> 39:26.010
Mother was just a maid.

39:26.980 --> 39:28.610
She was ordered to serve the Lord.

39:29.210 --> 39:30.490
Would she dare refuse?

39:33.010 --> 39:34.380
She did nothing wrong.

39:34.820 --> 39:36.900
Yin Qinglian poisoned her,

39:36.900 --> 39:38.210
torturing her to death.

39:38.820 --> 39:40.010
If it weren't for the letter

39:40.010 --> 39:41.490
hidden in her pillow,

39:43.420 --> 39:44.610
I'd still be in the dark.

39:45.130 --> 39:46.570
Was it Li Wenxun,

39:47.780 --> 39:48.860
or someone else

39:49.260 --> 39:51.210
from the Six Sects?

39:54.820 --> 39:55.860
Now, I no longer need

39:57.170 --> 39:59.010
to hide from that person,

39:59.490 --> 40:01.010
but I truly don't know who they were.

40:01.420 --> 40:02.686
Their skills were extraordinary,

40:02.940 --> 40:04.213
their movements were ghost-like,

40:04.420 --> 40:06.050
and their bodies were covered.

40:07.340 --> 40:09.050
I couldn't gauge
their martial arts origin.

40:13.530 --> 40:14.780
That's it?

40:18.690 --> 40:19.940
You were just a pawn.

40:20.340 --> 40:21.380
Nothing more to learn.

40:21.940 --> 40:23.340
Pay respects to your mother.

40:24.380 --> 40:25.690
Such a good cover

40:26.090 --> 40:27.170
deserves use.

40:27.170 --> 40:28.090
What do you mean?

40:32.010 --> 40:33.420
You conspired with Uncle Song,

40:34.050 --> 40:35.780
scheming for ten years.

40:36.380 --> 40:38.210
Whether your mother
was poisoned or not,

40:38.740 --> 40:40.690
you'd still go after the lord position.

40:41.090 --> 40:42.130
The man in black

40:42.130 --> 40:44.260
just provided a convenient excuse.

40:46.260 --> 40:47.900
Power, once gained,

40:49.050 --> 40:50.490
you should hold tightly.

40:57.260 --> 40:58.820
Our guess was correct.

40:59.490 --> 41:01.340
The man in black was indeed
from the Six Sects,

41:01.340 --> 41:03.650
hence knowing Song secrets.

41:03.650 --> 41:04.490
However,

41:04.650 --> 41:05.820
after all these plots,

41:06.340 --> 41:07.210
what is their goal?

41:08.770 --> 41:09.610
Young Master,

41:09.610 --> 41:10.530
should we

41:10.530 --> 41:11.820
tell Miss Cai?

41:12.820 --> 41:13.660
Not yet.

41:15.780 --> 41:16.620
Young Master,

41:17.090 --> 41:18.003
everything is prepared.

41:18.570 --> 41:19.860
Was the message spread?

41:20.690 --> 41:21.610
Young Master,

41:21.610 --> 41:23.340
with so many treasures,

41:23.340 --> 41:24.650
are you buying a city

41:24.650 --> 41:26.490
or building a new treasury?

41:26.490 --> 41:27.330
To Luoying Valley.

41:40.980 --> 41:42.210
You had a dream?

41:48.420 --> 41:49.530
I dreamed of Aunt.

41:51.980 --> 41:52.820
Cai Han,

41:53.380 --> 41:54.530
a year without seeing you,

41:54.980 --> 41:56.050
why are you so thin?

41:56.980 --> 41:57.980
Not eating well?

41:58.380 --> 42:00.820
No, I missed you.

42:01.380 --> 42:03.130
You even became a demoness.

42:04.490 --> 42:05.530
Are you impressed

42:05.530 --> 42:06.570
and happy

42:06.570 --> 42:07.490
about that?

42:07.490 --> 42:09.010
Yes.

42:09.010 --> 42:10.090
You're amazing.

42:11.690 --> 42:12.740
But Zhao,

42:13.420 --> 42:15.210
why did you elope with Ning

42:15.210 --> 42:17.260
and bring back Yuzhi?

42:17.900 --> 42:19.380
Yuzhi is handsome,

42:19.380 --> 42:20.673
and you don't need confinement.

42:21.130 --> 42:22.300
Eloping, my foot!

42:22.780 --> 42:24.900
I was righting
an injustice and saved him.

42:25.170 --> 42:26.380
There's plenty of injustice.

42:26.650 --> 42:27.940
Why save only him?

42:28.420 --> 42:29.690
Stop showing off.

42:31.170 --> 42:32.010
Where's Yuzhi?

42:32.010 --> 42:33.530
He worked so hard.

42:33.530 --> 42:35.650
He was with Lord Song last night.

42:35.650 --> 42:36.530
At the early Mao hour,

42:36.530 --> 42:37.996
he was already practicing.

42:38.210 --> 42:39.900
Almost six hours already.

42:42.820 --> 42:43.840
Zhao, where are you going?

42:43.980 --> 42:44.980
To find Yuzhi.

42:54.380 --> 42:56.180
(Wonton)

43:01.260 --> 43:02.300
Hello.

43:03.820 --> 43:04.660
Here.

43:04.820 --> 43:07.260
Authentic Spring Tofu Pudding. Try it.

43:08.010 --> 43:08.860
Thank you, Uncle.

43:08.860 --> 43:09.700
I've eaten already.

43:12.610 --> 43:15.340
After all these years,
you're the first man

43:15.340 --> 43:17.420
Manager Zhao brought back.

43:20.530 --> 43:21.756
Do you want to marry into here?

43:24.570 --> 43:26.530
Stop joking.

43:26.530 --> 43:28.420
Yuzhi is a prodigy.

43:28.980 --> 43:31.420
All the Six Sects will be under him.

43:31.820 --> 43:33.940
How could we keep him here?

43:38.490 --> 43:39.650
Another bowl, Uncle Douhua.

43:43.170 --> 43:44.420
Someone barged in here!

43:44.420 --> 43:45.260
Come with me!

43:47.300 --> 43:48.420
Let's go.

43:50.300 --> 43:51.140
Make way.

43:55.650 --> 43:56.490
Mr. Mu.

43:57.090 --> 43:57.980
Why are you here?

43:58.210 --> 43:59.050
Miss Cai,

43:59.540 --> 44:00.420
the Young Master

44:00.420 --> 44:02.780
came here to propose.

44:05.761 --> 44:16.421
=Generation to Generation=

44:35.181 --> 44:39.591
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

44:40.156 --> 44:44.771
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

44:45.111 --> 44:49.676
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

44:50.201 --> 44:54.501
♪Free to wander in the world♪

44:57.446 --> 45:02.146
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

45:02.671 --> 45:06.961
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

45:07.621 --> 45:11.651
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

45:11.966 --> 45:17.091
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

45:17.666 --> 45:22.476
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

45:22.691 --> 45:26.861
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

45:27.586 --> 45:31.521
♪I freely roam in the world♪

45:32.021 --> 45:37.296
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

46:00.026 --> 46:05.156
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

46:05.521 --> 46:09.891
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

46:10.156 --> 46:14.286
♪I freely roam in the world♪

46:14.471 --> 46:20.046
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
